\c 11
\s Ataria mai vaAhazia, anobata ushe hwaJudha
\p
\v 1 Zvino Ataria mai vaAhazia, wa- kati achiona kuti mwanakomana wake wafa, akasimuka, akaparadza vose vorudzi rwamambo.
\p
\v 2 Asi Jehoshebha mukunda wama- mbo Joramu, hanzvadzi yaAhazia, waka- tora Joashi mwanakomana waAhazia, akamuba pakati pavanakomana vamambo vaiurawa, iye nomureri wake, mumba mokuvata; vakamuvanza panaAtaria, nai- zvozvo haana kuurawa.
\v 3 Akagara naye akavanzwa mumba maJehovha makore matanhatu; Ataria akabata ushe panyika.
\p
\v 4 Zvino negore rechinomwe Jehoya- dha akatuma vanhu vakatora vakuru vamazana vavaKari navarindi vama- mbo, akauya navo kwaari mumba maJe- hovha, akaita sungano navo, akavapikisa mumba maJehovha, akavaratidza mwa- nakomana wamambo.
\v 5 Akavaraira, akati, "Munofanira kuita kudai, Imi munopinda neSabata, chetatu chenyu munofanira kuva varindi veimba yama- mbo;
\v 6 chimwe chetatu munofanira ku- mira pasuo rinonzi Suri; chimwe cheta- tuzve vanofanira kumira pasuo riri shure kwavarindi vamambo; saizvozvo munofanira kurinda imba, nokuidzivirira.
\p
\v 7 Mapoka enyu maviri, imi mose munobuda neSabata, munofanira kurinda imba yaJehovha muchikomba mambo.
\p
\v 8 Mukombe mambo, mumwe nomumwe akabata nhumbi dzokurwa nadzo muruoko rwake; Ani naani unopinda pakati pemisara, unofanira kuurawa; mugare namambo kana achibuda uye kana achipinda."
\p
\v 9 Vakuru vamazana vakaita zvose zvavakarairwa nomupristi Jehoyadha; mumwe nomumwe akatora vanhu vake, ivo vaifanira kupinda neSabata, naivo vaifanira kubuda neSabata, vakasvika kumupristi Jehoyadha.
\v 10 Mupristi akapa vakuru vamazana mapfumo nenhowo zvaiva zvamambo Dhavhidhi, zvakanga zviri mumba maJehovha.
\v 11 Zvino varindi vamambo vakamira mumwe nomumwe akabata nhumbi dzokurwa nadzo muruoko rwake, kubva kurutivi rworudyi rweimba kusvikira kurutivi rworuboshwe rweimba, napaaritari neimba, vakakomba mambo.
\v 12 Ipapo akabudisa mwanakomana wamambo, akamudzika korona, akamupa chipupuriro, vakamuita mambo, vakamuzodza; ndokuridza nhondo, vachiti
\p "Mambo ngaararame!"
\p
\v 13 Zvino Ataria wakati achinzwa mhere-mhere yavarindi vamambo navanhu, akapinda kuvanhu mumba maJehovha.
\v 14 Akatarira, ndokuona mambo amire pambiru, netsika yavo, navakuru navakanga vane hwamanda vamire kuna mambo; vanhu vose venyika vakafara, vakaridza hwamanda. Ipapo Ataria akabvarura nguo dzake, akadanidzira, achiti, "Ndamukirwa, ndamukirwa!"
\p
\v 15 Zvino mupristi Jehoyadha akaraira vakuru vamazana, vairaira hondo, akati kwavari, "Mubudisei pakati pemisara yavanhu; Ani naani unomutevera iye, munofanira kumuuraya nomunondo; nokuti mupristi wakati, `Ngaarege kuurayiwa mukati meimba yaJehovha.' "
\v 16 Naizvozvo vakamudzivirira nzira, akaenda nenzira yaipinda mabhiza nayo kumba kwamambo, ndokuurayirwapo.
\p
\v 17 ZNino khoyadha akaita sungano
\p pakati paJehovha namambo navanhu, kuti vave vanhu vaJehovha; uyewo pakati pamambo navanhu.
\v 18 Vanhu vose venyika vakaenda kumba kwaBhaari, vakaiputsa; vakaputsa kwazvo aritari dzake
\p nemifananidzo yake, vakauraya Matani mupristi waBhaari pamberi pearitari. Mupristi akagadza vatariri paimba yaJehovha.
\v 19 Akatora vakuru vamazana, navaKari, navarindi vamambo, navanhu vose venyika, vakaburusa mambo paimba yaJehovha, vakaenda kumba kwamambo nenzira yesuo ravarindi vamambo. Iye akagara pachigaro choushe chamadzimambo.
\v 20 Naizvozvo vanhu vose venyika vakafara, guta rikanyarara; vakauraya Ataria nomunondo paimba yamatnbo.
\p
\v 21 Jehoashi wakatanga kubata ushe ana makore manomwe.
